nto three different classes.\\r\\n\\r\\n**Arlima_ListRepository** \u2014 CRUD operations for the lists.\\r\\n\\r\\n**Arlima_VersionRepository** \u2014 CRUD operations for the list versions.\\r\\n\\r\\n**Arlima_ScheduledVersionRepository** \u2014 CRUD operations for scheduled list versions (extends VersionRepository).\\r\\n\\r\\n**Arlima_ListBuilder** \u2014 Class that can create a list object, following a set of instructions. \\r\\n\\r\\nExample on using the list builder:\\r\\n\\r\\n```php\\r\\n$list = Arlima_List::builder()\\r\\n          ->id(323) # list id\\r\\n          ->slug( 'my-list' ) # can be used instead of id()\\r\\n          ->import( $url )  # can be used instead of id() or slug()      \\r\\n          ->loadVersion(1234) # load articles belonging to version 1234\\r\\n          ->loadLatestVersion() # load latest published version\\r\\n          ->loadScheduledVersion(1234) # load articles from a scheduled version\\r\\n          ->loadPreview() # load latest preview version\\r\\n          ->includeFuturePosts()\\r\\n          ->build();\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\n- The functions `loadVersion()`, `loadLatestVersion()`, `loadScheduledVersion()` and `loadPreview()` can not be combined. \\r\\n- When loading loading a scheduled version a function call to `includeFuturePosts()` won't have any effect.\\r\\n- When calling `import()` none of the other functions (except `build()`) will have any effect.\\r\\n\\r\\nI have looked through the current list factory and placed its functions in one of the repositories\\r\\n\\r\\n```php\\r\\nArlima_ListRepository extends Arlima_AbstractRepositoryDB {\\r\\n   save()\\r\\n   load( $id_or_slug )\\r\\n   updated()\\r\\n   delete()\\r\\n   getListId( $slug )\\r\\n   loadListSlugs()\\r\\n}\\r\\n\\r\\nArlima_VersionRepository extends Arlima_AbstractRepositoryDB {\\r\\n   save($articles, $list_id, $preview=false)\\r\\n   loadVersions($limit=5) \/\/ get array with list versions, each version containing the articles\\r\\n   loadInfo() \/\/ Array with info about all saved versions array( array(verisonID, authorID, date), ... )\\r\\n   updateArticlePublishDate( $post )\\r\\n   updateArticle(...)\\r\\n   getLatestArticle($post_id);\\r\\n   loadListVersionsByPostId($post_id)\\r\\n   removeOldVersions($list_id, $num_versions_to_keep=10)\\r\\n}\\r\\n\\r\\nArlima_ScheduledVersionRepository extends Arlima_VersionRepository {\\r\\n   saveScheduledVersion($articles, $list_id, $date)\\r\\n   ...\\r\\n}\\r\\n\\r\\nArlima_AbstractRepositoryDB {  \\r\\n    get_result()\\r\\n    db_table()\\r\\n    install()\\r\\n    uninstall()\\r\\n}\\r\\n```\\r\\n\"},{\"url\":\"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/victorjonsson\/Arlima\/issues\/49\",\"repository_url\":\"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/victorjonsson\/Arlima\",\"labels_url\":\"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/victorjonsson\/Arlima\/issues\/49\/labels{\/name}\",\"comments_url\":\"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/victorjonsson\/Arlima\/issues\/49\/comments\",\"events_url\":\"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/victorjonsson\/Arlima\/issues\/49\/events\",\"html_url\":\"https:\/\/github.com\/victorjonsson\/Arlima\/issues\/49\",\"id\":40481073,\"number\":49,\"title\":\"Feature request: support scheduled lists\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"aaslun\",\"id\":555273,\"avatar_url\":\"https:\/\/avatars.githubusercontent.com\/u\/555273?v=3\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/aaslun\",\"html_url\":\"https:\/\/github.com\/aaslun\",\"followers_url\":\"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/aaslun\/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/aaslun\/following{\/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/aaslun\/gists{\/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/aaslun\/starred{\/owner}{\/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/aaslun\/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/aaslun\/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/aaslun\/repos\"